Definition: direct and obvious in meaning or reference
Example: often unpleasant; a pointed critique; a pointed allusion to what was going on; another pointed look in their direction
Synonyms: noun, attribute, pointedness, direct, and, obvious, in, meaning, or, reference, often, unpleasant, a, critique, allusion, to, what, was, going, on, another, look, their, direction
Category: adj.all
